window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The hunt is on. But who is the hunter, and who is the hunted?</b></p> <p>Ayleth and Terryn survived the Witchwood, but they're no closer to solving the mystery of the dead shade hunter. In their quest for answers, they discover that a witch has escaped through the Great Barrier and is leaving a trail of corpses in her wake.</p> <p>A murderous witch is only one of Ayleth's problems, however. Terryn, her infuriating and intriguing rival, will give his all to win their competition. And Kephan, their Outpost Master, conceals more than one dangerous secret.</p> <p>Worst of all, while pursuing a lead, Ayleth finds herself on the hunt for a three-year-old girl...a girl possessed by a unique and powerful shade.</p> <p>Suddenly, Ayleth must question the teachings of her Holy Order. Is it always right to kill humans possessed by shades? Even a child?</p>"; 
